          "settings": {
            "svg1": "",
            "image1": "shopify://shop_images/hp-section4-img1.avif",
            "text1": "<p><strong>1. Screentime limits are too easy to bypass</strong></p><p>Unfortunately, we all know what happens. A quick pincode and \"ignore\" button makes them ineffective in 2 seconds.</p>",
            "svg2": "",
            "image2": "shopify://shop_images/hp-section4-img2.avif",
            "text2": "<p><strong>2. Leaving your phone at home is unrealistic, most of the time</strong></p><p>Yes, we've been there, and it's just too extreme. You might even get lost in the woods. We literally did.</p>",
            "svg3": "",
            "image3": "shopify://shop_images/hp-section4-img3.avif",
            "text3": "<p><strong>3. Dumb phones lack the tools we love</strong></p><p>Nokia, we see you. You're amazingly cool and deserve a spot, but we love our maps, great camera, and a few fun & stupid videos just too much to make the switch</p>",
            "svg4": "",
